 	i have just checked it and you have three files that are loaded:
 	protman :  128 bytes
 	driver	: 9072 bytes
 	workgrp	: 4416 bytes
 >
 >q2:  if i have a novell ne2000 card, are the lsl and ipx drivers
 >     still needed?
 
 	no w4wg uses it's own drivers.
 >
